# Scripts Reference

Read the script header or `--help` for full usage. This rule maps script to purpose.

## Installation

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `install-rhoai-34.sh` | Full RHOAI 3.4 install (--skip-prerequisites, --skip-rhcl, --skip-maas, --channel, --enable-vllm-maas, --enable-observability, --postgres-connection, --skip-maas-db). Deploys POC PostgreSQL for MaaS by default, uses service-ca TLS, sets maasAuthPolicies. |
| `install-rhoai-33.sh` | Full RHOAI 3.3 install with all prerequisites (supports --skip-prerequisites, --skip-rhcl, --skip-maas, --channel) |
| `install-rhoai-minimal.sh` | Minimal RHOAI install (choose operators interactively) |
| `openshift-installer-master.sh` | OpenShift cluster installation on AWS |

## GPU & Hardware

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `create-gpu-machineset.sh` | Create GPU MachineSet on AWS (g6e, p5) |
| `create-hardware-profile.sh` | Create GPU HardwareProfile in a namespace |
| `fix-gpu-resourceflavor.sh` | Fix Kueue ResourceFlavor tolerations |
| `fix-hardware-profile.sh` | Fix hardware profile visibility in dashboard |

## Model Deployment

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `serve-model.sh` | Deploy model from S3/OCI with vLLM or llm-d |
| `deploy-llmd-model.sh` | Deploy LLMInferenceService for MaaS |
| `add-model-to-playground.sh` | Add model endpoint to GenAI playground |
| `setup-model-storage.sh` | Deploy MinIO for model storage |
| `download-model.sh` | Download HuggingFace model to S3 |
| `add-serving-runtime.sh` | Add custom runtimes (--preset omni for vLLM-Omni) |

## MaaS & Infrastructure

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `setup-maas.sh` | MaaS API gateway (auto-detects RHOAI version) |
| `setup-mcp-servers.sh` | Configure MCP servers for tool calling |
| `enable-dashboard-features.sh` | Enable Model Registry, GenAI Studio, etc. |

## Utility

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `cleanup-all.sh` | Destroy cluster and clean up all AWS resources |
| `manage-kubeconfig.sh` | Interactive kubeconfig management |
| `check-aws-prerequisites.sh` | Validate AWS setup before install |
